data.description: **Seller offering up to $9000 in closing costs to the buyer if under contract by Jan 18th** Wonderful location on the edge of Piedmont and Yukon in Buffalo Grove, a Village Verde neighborhood. This home was built in 2019 and has been meticulously taken care of. There is a large greenbelt right next to the home, giving this home extra space on one side! 3 bedrooms/2 bathrooms and 1458 sq feet. Tile floors throughout the entryway, kitchen, dining area and bathrooms with vinyl wood flooring in the large living room and carpets in all 3 bedrooms. One of the secondary bedrooms has a closet large enough to walk in--the current owners even have a dresser in there with plenty of space left for hanging clothes and shoes. Subway tile as the backsplash in the kitchen with a large island, gas stove and a walk-in pantry. The dining area would accommodate a table for at least 6-8 people. The backyard is fully fenced and has a covered patio, perfect for enjoying an evening outside in the shade. There is a splash pad at the end of the street, along with a volleyball court, basketball court and playground in the neighborhood. Legal address is Piedmont, OK but filters into Yukon schools
